Class TestManagementService

  • public class TestManagementService

      • removeExpiredComments

        public void removeExpiredComments(String issueKey,
                                  Date expirationDate)
                           throws IOException
        Removes all report comments before specified date (excluding date passed as parameter)
        Parameters:
        issueKey - the issue key for comments removing
        expirationDate - the date until which all comments are considered to be expired (excluded this specified date)
        Throws:
        IOException - exception throwing in the case of HttpClient problems
